Dubwool (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0831: Wooloo
Pokémon
#0833: Chewtle →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Dubwool (TCG Pocket).

Dubwool has been featured on 6 different cards since it debuted in the Sword & Shield expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Dubwool cards are normally Colorless-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Dubwool

Dubwool
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
